title: Slammin All-Body Band - Vocal Jazz Pop
description:
Source:  2005 CD

I can assure you have never heard music like this before unless you have heard these artists before.  - Big Papi



By Kenneth Murray

Astonishing ensemble jazz music April 23, 2007

Format:Audio CD
Slammin brings together 6 musicians who clearly are masters of each of their specialties, blending together to produce astonishing music that fully integrates each contribution. The most astonishing thing is that this music is not produced by any actual musical instrument, but simply the sounds that the body and voice make.

The only thing that is better, is actually seeing them produce it, which I've had the luck to do. I sat there crying from the beauty.
